name: Annicka
cleanBio: Specializing in the minimal melodic house subgenre, Annicka's sound knows no bounds as she fearlessly pushes herself to produce new music and master her craft in the electronic scene. Annicka has already shared stages with industry titans like «çME, Damian Lazarus, Keinemusik, Guy Gerber and CamelPhat. From the shores of Vagalume in Tulum to the desert of Burning Man in Black Rock City, she has performed across the globe gracing stages in Ibiza, New York City, spreading her infectious passion for her music. Annicka's passion for creating immersive musical experiences is palpable in her euphoric grooves, rhythmic beats, and entrancing melodies; she possesses an innate talent and a deep-seated love for the art form. Annicka effortlessly connects people, wanting to leave an indelible mark on the global electronic music scene and continue to grow as a true artist.
